<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Integrity Construction KC — Design Versions</title>
  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body { font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif; background: #1a1a1a; color: #fff; min-height: 100vh; }
    .picker { max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 3rem 2rem; }
    h1 { font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .subtitle { color: #999; margin-bottom: 3rem; font-size: 1rem; }
    .grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem; }
    .card { background: #2a2a2a; border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.75rem; transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s; text-decoration: none; color: #fff; display: block; }
    .card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.4); }
    .card-num { font-size: 0.75rem; color: #666; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .card h2 { font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .card p { font-size: 0.85rem; color: #999; line-height: 1.5; }
    .card .tag { display: inline-block; margin-top: 1rem; font-size: 0.7rem; padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem; border-radius: 50px; background: #333; color: #aaa; }
    .back { display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 2rem; color: #666; font-size: 0.85rem; text-decoration: none; }
    .back:hover { color: #fff; }
  </style>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="picker">
    <a href="../" class="back">← Back to main site</a>
    <h1>Design Versions</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">10 different takes on Integrity Construction KC. Click any to preview.</p>
    <div class="grid">
      <a href="v1-owner/" class="card">
        <div class="card-num">Version 01</div>
        <h2>Talk to the Owner</h2>
        <p>"I'm Jordan, and I'm the one you'll talk to about your project." Personal, direct, trust-first. His face is the first thing you see.</p>
        <span class="tag">personal trust</span>
      </a>
      <a href="v2-instant-price/" class="card">
        <div class="card-num">Version 02</div>
        <h2>Instant Price</h2>
        <p>Select fence type + enter linear feet = get a price estimate instantly. No waiting, no phone tag. Frictionless quoting.</p>
        <span class="tag">conversion</span>
      </a>
      <a href="v3-bigbutton/" class="card">
        <div class="card-num">Version 03</div>
        <h2>Big Buttons</h2>
        <p>Massive CTAs, huge text, high contrast. Three actions: Call Jordan, Get a Quote, See Our Work. Impossible to miss.</p>
        <span class="tag">accessibility</span>
      </a>
      <a href="v4-portfolio/" class="card">
        <div class="card-num">Version 04</div>
        <h2>Portfolio First</h2>
        <p>Lead with the work. Full-bleed project photos dominate. Let the craftsmanship sell itself before any copy.</p>
        <span class="tag">visual</span>
      </a>
      <a href="v5-trust/" class="card">
        <div class="card-num">Version 05</div>
        <h2>Trust & Reviews</h2>
        <p>Social proof heavy. Reviews front and center, star ratings, Trustpilot-style credibility. Let happy customers do the selling.</p>
        <span class="tag">social proof</span>
      </a>
      <a href="v6-family/" class="card">
        <div class="card-num">Version 06</div>
        <h2>Family Business</h2>
        <p>Jordan the family man. Supporting his wife, two kids, one on the way. Warm, human, community-rooted. People hire people they relate to.</p>
        <span class="tag">warmth</span>
      </a>
      <a href="v7-neighborhood/" class="card">
        <div class="card-num">Version 07</div>
        <h2>KC Neighborhood</h2>
        <p>Hyper-local KC pride. Service area map, neighborhood testimonials, "your neighbor's fence guy." Community over corporation.</p>
        <span class="tag">local</span>
      </a>
      <a href="v8-minimal/" class="card">
        <div class="card-num">Version 08</div>
        <h2>Clean Minimal</h2>
        <p>Ultra-clean, whitespace-heavy. One photo, one message, one CTA. Premium feel. Less noise, more action.</p>
        <span class="tag">simplicity</span>
      </a>
      <a href="v9-chat/" class="card">
        <div class="card-num">Version 09</div>
        <h2>Chat with Jordan</h2>
        <p>Conversational UI — feels like texting Jordan directly. Message-bubble style layout. "Hey, tell me about your fence project."</p>
        <span class="tag">innovative</span>
      </a>
      <a href="v10-before-after/" class="card">
        <div class="card-num">Version 10</div>
        <h2>Before & After</h2>
        <p>Dramatic transformation slider. Side-by-side before/after reveals. The most visually compelling proof of quality work.</p>
        <span class="tag">visual proof</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
